---
name: findings-report
version: 1.0.0
description: Multi-pass QA findings report template for FAIL/IN-FLIGHT updates.
format: markdown
required_variables:
  - generated_at
  - qa_pass
  - sprint_id
  - task_id
  - branch
  - commit
  - pr_number
  - verdict
  - merge_readiness
  - merge_reason
  - findings_blocking
  - findings_important
  - findings_minor
  - blocking_ids
  - blocking_findings_md
  - detailed_findings_md
  - next_action
  - action_owner
---
# QA Findings Update

