QA Pass: {{ qa_pass }}
Sprint/Task: {{ sprint_id }} / {{ task_id }}
Branch: `{{ branch }}`
Commit: `{{ commit }}`
PR: #{{ pr_number }}
Verdict: **{{ verdict }}**

## Machine Status (JSON)
```json
{
  "sprint": "{{ sprint_id }}",
  "task": "{{ task_id }}",
  "branch": "{{ branch }}",
  "commit": "{{ commit }}",
  "pr": "{{ pr_number }}",
  "verdict": "{{ verdict }}",
  "findings": {
    "blocking": "{{ findings_blocking }}",
    "important": "{{ findings_important }}",
    "minor": "{{ findings_minor }}"
  },
  "blocking_ids": "{{ blocking_ids }}",
  "merge_readiness": "{{ merge_readiness }}",
  "merge_reason": "{{ merge_reason }}",
  "next_action": "{{ next_action }}",
  "owner": "{{ action_owner }}"
}
```

